headline: McKesson Corporation Completes Acquisition of PRISM Vision Holdings, LLC
summary: IRVING, Texas, April 02, 2025--McKesson Corporation (NYSE: MCK) today announced the completion of its previously announced acquisition of a controlling interest in PRISM Vision Holdings, LLC, a leading provider of general ophthalmology and retina management services.
